<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 12:12:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亲巴勒斯坦抗议者在墨尔本酒店大堂骚扰加沙人质家人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-30/ty-article/pro-palestine-protesters-harass-family-of-gaza-hostages-in-melbourne-hotel-lobby/0000018c-1fc0-d9ef-abcd-1fe104ab0000</link><description>澳大利亚总理表示，“我对这些抗议者的行为感到震惊，并谴责他们。”自加沙战争开始以来，澳大利亚对以色列人和犹太人的敌意不断增加</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 11:54:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-30/ty-article/pro-palestine-protesters-harass-family-of-gaza-hostages-in-melbourne-hotel-lobby/0000018c-1fc0-d9ef-abcd-1fe104ab0000</guid></item><item><title>身患绝症的以色列母亲呼吁拜登帮助释放被哈马斯囚禁的女儿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/terminally-ill-israeli-mom-calls-on-biden-to-help-release-daughter-from-hamas-captivity/0000018c-1f8d-db78-adcc-bffd3a820000</link><description>一段广为流传的诺瓦狂欢节袭击事件视频显示，人质诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani) 被哈马斯恐怖分子抓获并骑摩托车带走。她的母亲在视频中告诉她，“请知道，我们已尽一切努力让你获释”</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 10:22:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/terminally-ill-israeli-mom-calls-on-biden-to-help-release-daughter-from-hamas-captivity/0000018c-1f8d-db78-adcc-bffd3a820000</guid></item><item><title>一个贝都因家庭请求以色列不要忘记他们在加沙被扣为人质的亲戚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/a-bedouin-family-is-asking-israel-to-not-forget-about-their-relatives-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018c-1f82-dc03-a9ec-1ffb98860000</link><description>10 月 7 日，贝都因家庭的四名成员在基布兹霍利特工作时被绑架。作为延长停火协议的一部分，家人希望 17 岁的艾莎和 18 岁的比拉尔能够在周四获释</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 10:06:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/a-bedouin-family-is-asking-israel-to-not-forget-about-their-relatives-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018c-1f82-dc03-a9ec-1ffb98860000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷恐怖袭击造成三名以色列人死亡、六人受伤；哈马斯附属袭击者被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/three-israelis-killed-in-jerusalem-attack-hamas-affiliated-assailants-shot-dead/0000018c-1f4a-da36-a1de-5f6fc5200000</link><description>枪击事件发生在耶路撒冷正门一个繁忙的公交车站。恐怖分子来自东耶路撒冷，其中一名此前曾在以色列被监禁</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 09:20:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/three-israelis-killed-in-jerusalem-attack-hamas-affiliated-assailants-shot-dead/0000018c-1f4a-da36-a1de-5f6fc5200000</guid></item><item><title>美国首位犹太裔国务卿、颇具争议的外交偶像亨利·基辛格去世，享年 100 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/henry-kissinger-first-u-s-jewish-secretary-of-state-and-contentious-icon-dies-at-100/0000018c-1ef0-db78-adcc-befc49f70000</link><description>基辛格是一名十几岁时与家人一起逃离纳粹德国的犹太人，在理查德·尼克松和杰拉尔德·福特总统领导下对全球事务产生了非凡的影响，既赢得了诽谤，也获得了诺贝尔和平奖</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 06:47:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/henry-kissinger-first-u-s-jewish-secretary-of-state-and-contentious-icon-dies-at-100/0000018c-1ef0-db78-adcc-befc49f70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的停火又迎来了战争的关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/as-the-truce-with-hamas-progresses-decision-time-for-israel-approaches/0000018c-1ce6-da36-a1de-5fe797c20000</link><description>至此，以色列既可以继续战斗，又可以进一步释放更多人质的幻想可能会破灭。由于哈马斯向以色列索要的价格，需要达成另一项协议，而且实现起来会更加困难</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 04:04:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/as-the-truce-with-hamas-progresses-decision-time-for-israel-approaches/0000018c-1ce6-da36-a1de-5fe797c20000</guid></item><item><title>“人道主义外交”现在将为以色列和哈马斯引领道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/humanitarian-diplomacy-will-now-lead-the-way-for-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-1d03-dc03-a9ec-1d7b00b00000</link><description>人道主义援助已成为这场运动的一个组成部分，这要归功于它以释放人质的形式为以色列做出的贡献，以及通过它至少可以实现战争目标的希望</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 04:03:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/humanitarian-diplomacy-will-now-lead-the-way-for-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-1d03-dc03-a9ec-1d7b00b00000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯声称对耶路撒冷恐怖袭击负责；埃及“努力”延长加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-live/12-israelis-four-thai-nationals-released-from-hamas-captivity-in-gaza/0000018c-1e28-db78-adcc-be7c50fb0007</link><description>耶路撒冷枪击事件造成三人死亡、六人受伤 ■ 卡塔尔：以色列与哈马斯停火将于周四继续 ■ 以色列收到将于周四释放的人质名单 ■ 周三从哈马斯囚禁中获释的 16 名人质：12 名以色列人和 4 名泰国国民 ■美国国务卿布林肯抵达以色列 ■ 自10月7日以来，以色列至少有1,200名平民和士兵丧生；加沙仍有超过 159 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙至少有 14,000 人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 03:55:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-live/12-israelis-four-thai-nationals-released-from-hamas-captivity-in-gaza/0000018c-1e28-db78-adcc-be7c50fb0007</guid></item><item><title>甘茨再次拯救了内塔尼亚胡，人们不会忘记</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gantz-saved-netanyahu-yet-again-it-wont-be-forgotten/0000018c-1c9a-da36-a1de-5fbff3590000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 02:42:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/gantz-saved-netanyahu-yet-again-it-wont-be-forgotten/0000018c-1c9a-da36-a1de-5fbff3590000</guid></item><item><title>加沙地带的巴勒斯坦人死亡人数太多了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-many-palestinians-dead-in-gaza-is-too-many/0000018c-1c99-db78-adcc-befde3500000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 02:31:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-many-palestinians-dead-in-gaza-is-too-many/0000018c-1c99-db78-adcc-befde3500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察，不要把手放在人质家属身上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-police-keep-your-hands-off-the-hostages-families/0000018c-1cc4-da36-a1de-5fe79ef00000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 02:22:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-police-keep-your-hands-off-the-hostages-families/0000018c-1cc4-da36-a1de-5fe79ef00000</guid></item><item><title>停火给加沙人带来了一些平静，但粮食短缺仍然存在，而且看不到解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/cease-fire-gives-gazans-some-quiet-but-no-solution-is-seen-to-the-food-shortage/0000018c-1d38-db78-adcc-bf7cfbe50000</link><description>流离失所的家庭前往近东救济工程处和世界粮食计划署运营的分发中心领取食品包。 “他们说这应该足够两周，但实际上坚持不了三天”</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 02:15:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/cease-fire-gives-gazans-some-quiet-but-no-solution-is-seen-to-the-food-shortage/0000018c-1d38-db78-adcc-bf7cfbe50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军在西岸行动中击毙伊斯兰圣战组织高级指挥官并逮捕 17 名巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/idf-kills-senior-islamic-jihad-commander-arrest-17-in-west-bank-operation/0000018c-1c94-d9ef-abcd-1eb5c1940000</link><description>在以色列军队和巴勒斯坦恐怖分子之间的交火中，两名分别为 15 岁和 9 岁的男孩被打死。一名军方消息人士告诉《国土报》，两人向部队投掷爆炸物</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 22:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/idf-kills-senior-islamic-jihad-commander-arrest-17-in-west-bank-operation/0000018c-1c94-d9ef-abcd-1eb5c1940000</guid></item><item><title>从哈马斯囚禁中获释的泰国国民正在努力应对创伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/released-from-hamas-captivity-thai-nationals-struggle-to-process-the-trauma/0000018c-1b77-dc03-a9ec-1f7f6f220000</link><description>获释的农业工人面临一系列特殊挑战，包括语言障碍和没有家人迎接他们。但他们很快就会在泰国与亲人团聚，许多人说他们想回到以色列</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 20:23:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/released-from-hamas-captivity-thai-nationals-struggle-to-process-the-trauma/0000018c-1b77-dc03-a9ec-1f7f6f220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列首席军事审查员抱怨内塔尼亚胡的压力和解雇威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-chief-military-censor-complains-of-pressure-threats-of-dismissal-from-netanyahu/0000018c-1b7d-dd4b-a38c-1f7f489c0000</link><description>几周前，内塔尼亚胡向首席军事审查员谈及收紧有关取消需要审查批准的材料资格的政策</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 19:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-chief-military-censor-complains-of-pressure-threats-of-dismissal-from-netanyahu/0000018c-1b7d-dd4b-a38c-1f7f489c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正在调查哈马斯声称比巴斯母子在加沙被杀的说法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-looking-into-hamas-claim-that-bibas-mother-and-sons-killed-in-gaza/0000018c-1c01-dc03-a9ec-1c7be0f40000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日 Bibas 一家被绑架以来，Shiri 抱着她的两个孩子被恐怖分子包围的视频被发布，他们已成为战争的象征</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 19:05:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/israel-looking-into-hamas-claim-that-bibas-mother-and-sons-killed-in-gaza/0000018c-1c01-dc03-a9ec-1c7be0f40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的风暴即将来临</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-29/ty-article/.highlight/the-storm-is-coming-for-netanyahu/0000018c-1c2d-dc03-a9ec-1c7f8a450000</link><description>以色列的政治分歧在 10 月 7 日与哈马斯的战争开始时暂时被掩盖，现在又重新公开化。一场新生运动的兴起几乎肯定会演变成更大的运动</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 18:52:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-29/ty-article/.highlight/the-storm-is-coming-for-netanyahu/0000018c-1c2d-dc03-a9ec-1c7f8a450000</guid></item><item><title>释放具有以色列公民身份的巴勒斯坦囚犯导致阿拉伯以色列人陷入困境</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/release-of-palestinian-prisoners-with-israeli-citizenship-causes-dilemma-for-arab-israelis/0000018c-1b72-dc03-a9ec-1f7bf7540000</link><description>几十年来，以色列政府一直拒绝在人质交易中释放具有以色列公民身份的巴勒斯坦安全囚犯。随着预计与哈马斯交换的囚犯名单公布，其中包括约 20 名以色列人，社区中许多人担心这是政府试图将他们与恐怖组织联系起来</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 18:50:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/release-of-palestinian-prisoners-with-israeli-citizenship-causes-dilemma-for-arab-israelis/0000018c-1b72-dc03-a9ec-1f7bf7540000</guid></item><item><title>意大利犹太人准备游行反对反犹太主义，拉比遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/rabbi-assaulted-as-italian-jews-prepare-to-march-against-antisemitism/0000018c-1b30-dc03-a9ec-1f7b041f0000</link><description>米兰当代犹太文献中心主席说，至少在过去十年里，我们在意大利还没有看到过这种程度的反犹太主义。自 10 月 7 日以来，意大利反犹太主义显着增加——这是全球反犹太事件激增的一部分</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 16:20:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/rabbi-assaulted-as-italian-jews-prepare-to-march-against-antisemitism/0000018c-1b30-dc03-a9ec-1f7b041f0000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯前往以色列和约旦河西岸，争取延长加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/blinken-heads-to-israel-west-bank-in-bid-to-extend-gaza-cease-fire/0000018c-1b97-dd4b-a38c-1f9799ea0000</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯致力于防止以色列和哈马斯之间的战争在整个中东地区扩大，并帮助带头努力增加对加沙地带的人道主义援助</description><pubDate>Wed, 29 Nov 2023 16:09:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-29/ty-article/.premium/blinken-heads-to-israel-west-bank-in-bid-to-extend-gaza-cease-fire/0000018c-1b97-dd4b-a38c-1f9799ea0000</guid></item></channel></rss>